[u'Director of Product Management, Performance Audio
Knowles Electronics - Mountain View, CA
June 2016 to Present
• In charge of MEMS microphone Share, Revenue, Profit growth at Samsung, LG and Japanese customers. Led new product introduction, design-in and ramp-up. Achieved 100% share at Samsung’s 2017 and 2018 flagship smartphone models and over 70% account share penetrations;
• Planned and executed impactful “Multi-Mic Adoption” campaign in Smartphones, Notebooks and IoT segments, by combining microphone with audio-processing software as a service. Achieved $15M in incremental revenue in 2017 and successfully increased the number of microphones per smartphone at Huawei, VIVO, OPPO, OnePlus and hTC. Presented bi-monthly progress directly to the CEO;
