• Led the collaborations with display manufacturers (Samsung Display, Sharp, Japan Display, LG Display, Tianma, BoE, Innolux, AUO, etc.) and touch panel module vendors to develop cutting-edge touch screen technologies, including Hybrid In-Cell, Full In-Cell, Force Sensing and flexible OLED with integrated touch sensors.", u'Product Marketing Manager
